{"tid":834111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【多相】【高鐵通車】敵不過中秋黃雨   西九高鐵站多處地方漏水","createTime":"2018-09-24T03:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T04:28:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb33a96c65fd7bada510788852dee591002a54ad","tid":834111,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"今天早上一場豪雨，高鐵西九龍站再現漏水。《毒果》記者在B2層餐廳「堂前食坊」發現地下有大灘水漬及最少2處滴水，現場亦放了「小心地滑」的警告牌。由於食肆沒有上蓋，故不少途經行人都好奇水滴從何而降。有工人知道記者拍攝，不發一言，但用身體語言暗示，水滴很有可能是從天幕滴下來。另外，高鐵西九龍站頂層亦有兩處漏水。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537759472_e0dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537759472_e0dd.jpg&h=cf0a61a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537759479_e62f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537759479_e62f.jpg&h=66b091c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537759479_f7ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537759479_f7ea.jpg&h=0c66b95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537759472_9b00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537759472_9b00.jpg&h=fe9d9576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537759472_288b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537759472_288b.jpg&h=df515210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/